file1.full_code:
t = int(input())
digits = "0123456789ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ"
for i in range(t):
    n, k = map(int, input().split())
    if n == 0:
        print("0")
        continue
    ans = ""
    while n > 0:
        r = n % k
        ans = digits[r] + ans
        n //= k
    print(ans)

file2.full_code:
digit = "0123456789ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ"
t = int(input())
for _ in range(t):
    n, k = map(int, input().split()) 
    if n == 0:
        result = "0"
    else:
        result = ""
        temp_n = n      
        while temp_n > 0:
            remainder = temp_n % k
            result = digit[remainder] + result
            temp_n //= k          
    print(result)
